com.bigdata.bop.fed

Class AllocationContextKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.bop.fed.AllocationContextKey

  • public abstract class AllocationContextKey
extends Object
    The allocation context key groups together allocations onto the same direct ByteBuffers. There are different implementations depending on how it makes sense to group data data for a given query.
    See Also:
    DirectBufferPoolAllocator.IAllocationContext
